products.name: Raisin Bran
products.description: The Greatest Cereal of ALL TIME. Highly disrespected and underrated. A must have staple of every American Pantry. 11/10

products.name: Honey Bunches of Oats
products.description: A King of Cereals. Can be found at your local Costco for a low price or individually sold at your local market. Top Tier with fruits. 9/10

products.name: Special K: Strawberry
products.description: Not an old person's cereal. This cereal is notorious for being a cereal that only older individuals can enjoy. But this is a blasphemous accusation. This cereal can be enjoyed by any and all who roam this Earth especially when combined with Raisin Bran. 8/10 alone...12/10 with Raisin Bran

products.name: Honey Nut Cherrios
products.description: Honey Nut Cherrios are good for your heart and your soul. Nothing more needs to be said 10/10

products.name: Reeses Puffs Cereal
products.description: Reeses Puffs, Reeses Puffs, PEANUT BUTTER CHOCOLATE FLAVOR! An iconic jingle. Never had these before but 9/10 for the jingle.

products.name: Froot Loops
products.description: Delicious Cereal that can be enjoyed dry or with your preferred type of milk. Featured in an iconic scene of the Oscar-Winning Film: Get Out. 10/10

products.name: Cinnamon Toast Crunch
products.description: Cinnamon and Sugar can do no wrong. An elite experience with cinnamilk at the bottom. Bonus Points for the cannibalistic toasts. 10/10

products.name: Frosted Flakes
products.description: Sugar and Corn is as American as it can get. Combined with a muscular Tiger who loves sports its an instant recipe for success. 8/10

products.name: Lucky Charms
products.description: Marshmellows lack consistency when mixed with the milk. The grains are very subpar and the milk at the end is disgusting. -4/10

products.name: Frosted Mini Wheats
products.description: Perfect blend of sugar and grains that get better with milk. An unforgettable experinence with subpar commercial branding. 8/10

products.name: Fruity Pebbles
products.description: TV show turned into iconic cereal is the rebranding that no one saw coming. Cereal is delicious but it can't stay in the milk for too long. 9/10

products.name: Cookie Crisp
products.description: Cookies and Milk are like Yin and Yang. But not this one -5/10
